Report bugs: https://pagure.io/teamsilverblue/issues

User data saved in ~/.var/app

Runtimes in /var/lib/flatpak/runtimes
	derived runtimes use hard links to source to save space
	use 'du -hs' to see space used

Point to WAyland socket
	flatpak [--user] run --socket=wayland your-app
		socket = /run/user/<user id>/wayland-0

Manage permissions: Flatseal

Applications {{{1

list
	show installed apps and runtimes


Remotes {{{1

remotes
	list configured remotes

remote-add <options> <repo file or URL>
	flatpak --user remote-add --if-not-exists flathub https://flathub.org/repo/flathub.flatpakrepo

flatpak search
	search packages at remotes

List packages at remote - not a search
	flatpak remote-ls flathub



flatpak --user update && flatpak --user search atom

Show package details
flatpak remote-info flathub io.atom.Atom


Install & Manage {{{1

install
    flatpak --user install flathub io.atom.Atom

search
    flatpak remote-ls --app --user flathub <pattern>
    flatpak search <pattern>


list
    List installed runtimes and packages
    -d  detailed

    flatpak list -d 

info
    flatpak info --show-permissions
    
ps
    list running instances and runtimes


desktop files location
	system
		/var/lib/flatpak/exports/share/applications/
	user
		.local/share/applications/


